quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Ndahiriye (ku bamalayika bahagaze) ku mirongo itunganye (basenga)
  37,2,No ku (bamalayika) bajyana ibicu (babyerekeza aho Allah ashaka)
  37,3,No ku (bamalayika) basoma (amagambo ya Allah) basingiza (Nyagasani wabo)
  37,4,"Mu by’ukuri, Imana yanyu ni imwe"
  37,5,"Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati ya byo, akaba na Nyagasani w’uburasirazuba bwose"
  37,6,"Mu by’ukuri, ikirere cyegereye isi twagitakishije inyenyeri"
  37,7,Tunakirinda buri shitani ryose ryigometse (dukoresheje ibishashi by’umuriro)
  37,8,"Ntirishobora kumviriza (ibivugwa n’abamalayika) mu ijuru, kubera ko riterwa (ibishashi) mu mpande zose"
  37,9,Bigamije kuryirukana. Kandi (no ku munsi w’imperuka) rizahanishwa ibihano bihoraho
  37,10,Usibye iribashije kwiba (ibanga) bwangu nuko rigakurikizwa ibishashi by’umuriro
  37,11,Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) babaze (abahakanyi b’i Maka) niba iremwa ryabo ari ryo rikomeye kurusha ibyo twaremye (ibirere n’isi ndetse n’imisozi). Mu by’ukuri twabaremye mu ibumba rimatira
  37,12,Ahubwo uratangazwa (no kuba bahakana izuka) ndetse banannyega (ubutumwa bwawe)
  37,13,N’iyo bibukijwe (amagambo ya Allah) ntacyo bibamarira
  37,14,N’ iyo babonye igitangaza (giturutse kwa Allah) baragisuzugura
  37,15,"Maze bakavuga bati \"Iki si ikindi usibye ko ari uburozi bugaragara"
  37,16,Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka ndetse n’amagufa (akabora) tuzazurwa koko
  37,17,N’abakurambere bacu (bazazurwa) se
  37,18,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yego muzazurwa, kandi muzaba musuzuguritse"
  37,19,"Mu by’ukuri, impanda izavuzwa rimwe, maze (bazurwe) babone (ibyo basezeranijwe)"
  37,20,"Nuko bavuge bati \"Mbega ishyano tubonye ! Uyu ni umunsi w’ibarura n’ibihembo"
  37,21,Uyu ni wo munsi w’urubanza mwajyaga muhinyura
  37,22,"(Abamalayika bazababwira) bati \"Mukoranye inkozi z’ibibi n’abambari bazo ndetse n’ibyo basengaga"
  37,23,"Bitari Allah, maze muberekeze mu nzira ibaganisha mu muriro ugurumana"
  37,24,"Munabahagarike kuko mu by’ukuri, bagomba (kubanza) kubazwa"
  37,25,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Byagenze bite ko mudatabarana (nk’uko mwabigenzaga ) ku isi"
  37,26,Ahubwo kuri uwo munsi bazaba baciye bugufi (basuzuguritse)
  37,27,Nuko bamwe bahindukirirane abandi babazanye
  37,28,"Bavuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, ni mwe mwatugeragaho muduhatira ubuyobe"
  37,29,"Babasubize bati \"Ahubwo ntabwo mwari abemeramana"
  37,30,Kandi nta bubasha twari tubafiteho; ahubwo mwari abantu barengera (imbibi za Allah)
  37,31,None ijambo (ry’ibihano) rya Nyagasani wacu ridusohoreyeho ko mu by’ukuri (tugomba) gusogongera (ibihano)
  37,32,"Twarabayobeje kuko mu by’ukuri, natwe twari twarayobye"
  37,33,Kuri uwo munsi bose bazaba bafatanyije ibihano
  37,34,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugenza inkozi z’ibibi"
  37,35,"Kuko iyo babwirwaga ko nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse Allah, baribonaga"
  37,36,"Bakanavuga bati \"Ese koko tureke imana zacu kubera umusizi w’umusazi"
  37,37,Ahubwo (Intumwa Muhamadi ) yazanye ukuri inahamya intumwa (zayibanjirije)
  37,38,"Mu by’ukuri, mwe (ababangikanyamana ) mugiye gusogongera ibihano bibabaza"
  37,39,Kandi nta kindi muri buhemberwe kitari ibyo mwakoreye
  37,40,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,41,Abo bazahabwa amafunguro azwi (mu ijuru)
  37,42,Imbuto; kandi bazaba bubashywe
  37,43,Mu busitani bwuje inema (Ijuru)
  37,44,Bari ku bitanda berekeranye
  37,45,Bazengurutswamo ibirahuri by’ibinyobwa byiza
  37,46,"Byererana, biryoheye ababinywa"
  37,47,Nta ngaruka bizabagiraho ndetse nta n’ubwo bizatuma bata ubwenge
  37,48,"Kandi bazaba bafite abagore biyubashye, b’amaso meza manini"
  37,49,Bameze nk’amagi yarinzwe neza
  37,50,Maze bamwe bahindukire barebe abandi babazanye
  37,51,"Umwe muri bo azavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, nari mfite inshuti magara (ku isi)"
  37,52,"Yajyaga ivuga iti \"Ese wowe koko uri mu bemera (izuka)"
  37,53,"Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka n’amagufwa (akabora), tuzabazwa ibyo twakoze koko"
  37,54,"Avuge ati \"Ese mushobora kureba (mu muriro)"
  37,55,Nuko arebe amubone hagati mu muriro ugurumana
  37,56,"Avuge ati \"Ndahiye ku izina rya Allah! Wari hafi yo kunyobya"
  37,57,"Iyo bitaza kuba ku bw’ingabire ya Nyagasani wanjye, nanjye nari kuba mu bazanywe (mu muriro kimwe nawe)"
  37,58,"(Abazaba bari mu ijuru bazavuga bati)\"Ese ntabwo tuzongera gupfa"
  37,59,"Usibye gusa urupfu rwacu rwa mbere, ndetse nta n’ubwo tuzahanwa (nyuma y’uko twinjiye mu ijuru)"
  37,60,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi ni intsinzi ihambaye"
  37,61,"Ku bw’ibyo, ngaho abakora (ibyiza) nibakore"
  37,62,"Ese kwakirwa gutyo niko kwiza, cyangwa (kwakirizwa) igiti cya cya Zaqum(ni byo byiza)"
  37,63,"Mu by’ukuri, (icyo giti ) twakigize ikigeragezo ku bahakanyi"
  37,64,Ni igiti gishibuka mu ndiba y’umuriro ugurumana
  37,65,Imbuto zacyo zimeze nk’imitwe y’amashitani
  37,66,"Mu by’ukuri, bazazirya bazuzuze inda"
  37,67,Maze barenzeho uruvange rw’amazi yatuye
  37,68,Hanyuma igarukiro ryabo rizabe mu muriro ugurumana
  37,69,"Mu by’ukuri, basanze abakurambere babo barayobye"
  37,70,Nuko nabo bihutira kugera ikirenge mu cyabo
  37,71,Kandi rwose abenshi mu babayeho mbere yabo barayobye
  37,72,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, twaranaboherereje ababurizi"
  37,73,Ngaho reba uko iherezo ry’ababuriwe ryagenze
  37,74,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,75,"Mu by’ukuri, Nuhu yaratwiyamabaje kandi ni twe beza bo kwiyambazwa"
  37,76,Nuko tumurokorana n’abantu be mu makuba ahambaye
  37,77,Maze dusigaza abamukomokaho
  37,78,Tunamuha kuzasigara avugwa neza mu bazabaho nyuma ye
  37,79,Amahoro ni abe kuri Nuhu mu biremwa byose
  37,80,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  37,81,"Mu by’ukuri, yari umwe mu bagaragu bacu b’abemeramana (twarokoye)"
  37,82,Hanyuma turoha abandi (bahakanye)
  37,83,"Mu by’ukuri, no mu bamukurikije harimo Ibrahimu"
  37,84,Ubwo yaganaga Nyagasani we n’umutima ukeye
  37,85,"Ubwo yabwiraga se n’abantu be ati \"Ibi musenga ni ibiki"
  37,86,Ese murashaka gusenga ibigirwamana mwihimbiye muretse Allah
  37,87,Ese mutekereza iki kuri Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose
  37,88,Nuko ( Ibrahimu ) yitegereza inyenyeri
  37,89,"Maze aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ndarwaye\" (Ibyo yabikoze ari amayeri yo kugira ngo asigare aho basengeraga ibigirwamana byabo kugira ngo abijanjagure, ndetse no kugira ngo atajyana nabo mu mihango yabo ya gipagani)"
  37,90,Nuko barahindukira barigendera
  37,91,"Maze yinyabya ku bigirwamana byabo, nuko aravuga ati \"Ese ntimurya (aya mafunguro mwateguriwe)"
  37,92,Bite byanyu ko mutavuga
  37,93,Maze arabyadukira abijanjaguza ukuboko kwe kw’iburyo
  37,94,Nuko (ba babangikanyamana) bagaruka bamugana bihuta
  37,95,"Arababwira ati \"Ese musenga ibyo mwihangiye"
  37,96,"Kandi Allah yarabaremye, mwe n’ibyo mwikorera"
  37,97,"Baravuga bati \"Nimumwubakire itanura maze mumujugunye mu muriro ugurumana"
  37,98,"Bamucuriye umugambi mubisha, nuko turabasuzuguza"
  37,99,"Nuko (amaze kurokoka umuriro) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ngannye kwa Nyagasani wanjye, azanyobora"
  37,100,Nyagasani wanjye! Mpa (umwana ) uzaba umwe mu ntungane
  37,101,Nuko tumuha inkuru nziza yo (kuzabyara) umuhungu witonda (ari we Isimayili)
  37,102,"Maze (umuhungu we) amaze kugera aho bagendana, (ise) aravuga ati \"Mwana wanjye! Mu by’ukuri, narose nkubaga (ngutangaho igitambo kwa Allah), mbwira uko ubibona?\" Aravuga ati \"Dawe! Kora icyo wategetswe, Allah nabishaka uzansanga mu bihangana"
  37,103,"Nuko bombi bamaze kumvira (itegeko rya Allah), (Ibrahimu) amuryamisha hasi yubitse umutwe (kugira ngo amubage)"
  37,104,"Maze turamuhamagara tuti \"Yewe Ibrahimu"
  37,105,"Rwose wakabije inzozi. Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko duhemba abakora neza"
  37,106,"Mu by’ukuri, iki ni cyo kigeragezo kigaragara"
  37,107,Nuko tumucunguza igitambo gihambaye (intama)
  37,108,Tunamuha kuzasigara avugwa neza mubazabaho nyuma ye
  37,109,Amahoro ni abe kuri Ibrahimu
  37,110,Uko ni ko tugorerera abakoze neza
  37,111,"Mu by’ukuri, (Ibrahimu) yari umwe mu bagaragu bacu b’abemera"
  37,112,"Kandi twamuhaye inkuru nziza (yo kuzabyara) Isihaka, akaba umuhanuzi (ndetse akaba n’umwe) mu ntungane"
  37,113,Nuko we na Isihaka tubaha imigisha. No mu rubyaro rwabo harimo abakora ibyiza ndetse n’abihemukira ku buryo bugaragara
  37,114,Kandi rwose Musa na Haruna twabahaye ingabire (y’ubutumwa)
  37,115,Maze tubarokorana n’abantu babo amakuba ahambaye (yo kurohama)
  37,116,Turanabatabara nuko baba ari bo batsinda
  37,117,Nuko tubaha igitabo (Tawurati) gisobanutse
  37,118,Tunabayobora inzira igororotse
  37,119,Kandi twanabahaye kuzasigara bavugwa neza mu bazabaho nyuma yabo
  37,120,Amahoro nabe kuri Musa na Haruna
  37,121,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  37,122,Rwose bombi bari mu bagaragu bacu b’abemera
  37,123,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, Iliyasi yari umwe mu ntumwa"
  37,124,"Ubwo yabwiraga abantu be ati \"Ese ntimutinya (Allah)"
  37,125,Ese musenga (ikigirwamana) Ba’ala muretse Umuremyi uhebuje
  37,126,"Allah, Nyagasani wanyu akaba na Nyagasani w’abakurambere banyu"
  37,127,"Nuko (Iliyasi) baramuhinyura. Mu by’ukuri, bazazanwa (kugira ngo bahanwe)"
  37,128,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,129,Twanamuhaye kuzasigara avugwa neza mu bazabaho nyuma ye
  37,130,Amahoro nabe kuri Iliyasi n’ab’iwe
  37,131,"Mu by’ukuri, uko ni ko tugororera abakoze neza"
  37,132,Mu by’ukuri (Iliyasi) yari umwe mu bagaragu bacu b’abemera
  37,133,Kandi rwose Lutwi yari umwe mu ntumwa
  37,134,Ubwo twamurokoranaga n’ab’iwe bose
  37,135,Usibye gusa umukecuru (umugore we) wabaye mubasigaye (mu bihano)
  37,136,Hanyuma abandi (bo mu mudugudu wa Sodoma) turabarimbura
  37,137,Kandi rwose mubanyuraho (ku matongo yabo) mu gitondo
  37,138,Ndetse na nijoro. Ese ntimutekereza
  37,139,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, Yunusu yari umwe mu ntumwa"
  37,140,Wibuke ubwo yahungiraga mu bwato bwuzuye (abantu n’ibintu)
  37,141,"Maze (akemera) kuba umwe mu batombora (kugira ngo bamenye urohwa mu nyanja), nuko aratsindwa (aba ari we uyirohwamo)"
  37,142,Nuko ifi iramumira kuko yari yakoze igikorwa kigayitse (cyo gusiga abantu be atabiherewe uburenganzira na Allah)
  37,143,Iyo ataza kuba ari umwe mu basingiza Allah
  37,144,Yari kuguma mu nda yayo kugeza ku munsi (abantu) bazazurirwaho
  37,145,Ariko twamujugunye ku nkombe ameze nk’umurwayi
  37,146,Maze dutegeka ko (aho yari ari) hamera uruyuzi rwera ibihaza kugira ngo ajye abirya
  37,147,Nuko tumwohereza ku bantu ibihumbi ijana cyangwa banarenga
  37,148,"Maze baremera, nuko tubaha umunezero w’igihe gito"
  37,149,"Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) babaze uti \"Ese Nyagasani wawe afite abakobwa gusa, hanyuma bo bakagira abahungu"
  37,150,Cyangwa twaremye abamalayika b’abakobwa babireba (ikaba ari yo mpamvu bavuga ko abamalayika ari igitsina gore)
  37,151,"Mu by’ukuri, no mu binyoma byabo (ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) baravuga (bati)"
  37,152,"Allah yarabyaye (bavugaga ko abamalayika ari abakobwa ba Allah)\" Nyamara rwose ni abanyabinyoma"
  37,153,Nonese (ni ukubera iki) yaba yarahisemo abakobwa mu kimbo cy’abahungu
  37,154,Ese mwabaye mute? Amahitamo yanyu ashingira kuki
  37,155,Ese ntimutekereza
  37,156,Cyangwa mufite ibimenyetso bigaragara
  37,157,"Ngaho nimuzane igitabo cyanyu, niba muri abanyakuri"
  37,158,"Kandi banashyize isano hagati ye (Allah) n’amajini, nyamara amajini yo azi neza ko azazanwa (imbere ya Allah kugira ngo acirwe urubanza)"
  37,159,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,160,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera (ni bo batajya bagira ibyo bamwitirira)
  37,161,"Bityo, mu by’ukuri mwe (ababangikanyamana) ndetse n’ibyo musenga bitari Allah"
  37,162,Nta n’umwe (mu bemeramana) mushobora kuyobya
  37,163,Uretse abazajya mu muriro ugurumana
  37,164,Kandi nta n’umwe muri twe (abamalayika) udafite umwanya uzwi (mu ijuru)
  37,165,"Mu by’ukuri, twe (abamalayika) dutonda imirongo (dusenga nk’uko Abayislamu babigenza)"
  37,166,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, ni twe dusingiza (Allah)"
  37,167,"(Kandi mu by’ukuri, ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) bajyaga bavuga bati"
  37,168,Iyo tuza kugira urwibutso nk’urw’abo hambere (mbere y’uko intumwa Muhamadi ihabwa ubutumwa)
  37,169,Mu by’ukuri twari kuba abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,170,Nyamara (nyuma y’uko Qor’an ibagezeho) barayihakanye kandi vuba aha bazamenya (ukuri)
  37,171,"Kandi rwose, isezerano ryacu ryaje mbere ku bagaragu bacu b’intumwa"
  37,172,"Ko mu by’ukuri, ari bo bazatsinda"
  37,173,"Kandi ko mu by’ukuri, ingabo zacu ari zo zizatsinda"
  37,174,Bityo rero (yewe Muhamadi) birengagizeho igihe gito
  37,175,"Unabahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,176,Ese ibihano byacu ni byo bashaka kwihutisha
  37,177,"Bityo, ubwo bizamanukira hafi yabo, kizaba ari igitondo kibi kuri babandi baburiwe"
  37,178,"Bityo, birengagize igihe gito (yewe Muhamadi)"
  37,179,"Unabahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,180,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Nyagasani wawe, Nyagasani Nyiricyubahiro! Ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,181,Kandi amahoro nabe ku ntumwa
  37,182,"Kandi ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"